"""Test X without any other column than cutoff_time."""
X = self.X
del X['id1']
timeseries = self.timeseries
del timeseries['id1']
array = cutoff_window_sequences(X, timeseries, window_size=3)
expected_array = np.array([[[12, 32], [13, 33], [14, 34]], [[14, 34], [15, 
    35], [16, 36]]])
assert_allclose(array, expected_array)
